You and John left it flat.

1076
01:25:17,212 --> 01:25:19,043
But I thought surely he was here.

1077
01:25:19,147 --> 01:25:21,980
Well, if he were, he doesn't know
any more about it than Huck does.

1078
01:25:22,050 --> 01:25:25,144
Not as much.
You are the one who is needed, Stephanie.

1079
01:25:25,220 --> 01:25:26,551
Well, that's impossible.

1080
01:25:26,654 --> 01:25:29,646
Why? Just because you and John
are in love with each other?

1081
01:25:29,724 --> 01:25:33,251
Don't be fantastic, Huck.
John isn't in love with me.

1082
01:25:35,096 --> 01:25:37,894
Is it fantastic when a man
is eating his heart out for you?

1083
01:25:37,999 --> 01:25:40,160
When your name is continually on his lips?

1084
01:25:40,235 --> 01:25:42,100
When he stands around
dark street corners

1085
01:25:42,203 --> 01:25:43,932
just to get a glimpse of you?

1086
01:25:44,038 --> 01:25:45,665
- He doesn't.
- He does, and more.

1087
01:25:45,740 --> 01:25:48,903
Everyone around here knows it
but you, Stephanie.

1088
01:25:49,010 --> 01:25:50,341
And maybe John.

1089
01:25:50,411 --> 01:25:53,744
- But he's always quarreling with me.
- Well, what more can you ask?

1090
01:25:53,848 --> 01:25:57,841
Oh, that's nothing. People in love
are always quarreling with each other.

1091
01:25:57,919 --> 01:26:00,114
Now you take Liz and myself for instance.

1092
01:26:00,221 --> 01:26:02,086
Liz? Who is this Liz?

1093
01:26:02,423 --> 01:26:05,392
Oh, a little country girl from back home
that I'm thinking of marrying.

1094
01:26:05,460 --> 01:26:09,089
You know, big feet, dumb, simple.
Oh, very simple.

1095
01:26:10,031 --> 01:26:13,523
Well, the simple and dumb ones
make the best wives sometimes.

1096
01:26:14,135 --> 01:26:17,730
Well, forgetting about this girl of Huck's
from back home, with the big feet,

1097
01:26:17,805 --> 01:26:20,035
what about Roberta? What about John?

1098
01:26:20,108 --> 01:26:23,441
Yes, Stephanie, you must come back
for Aunt Minnie's sake.

1099
01:26:25,280 --> 01:26:27,646
No, I'm sorry. I can't.

1100
01:26:27,982 --> 01:26:29,813
Stephanie, you must.

1101
01:26:30,051 --> 01:26:31,382
Come in.

1102
01:26:31,920 --> 01:26:33,478
