<i>The sort of thing your jealous friends</i>
<i>would love to spill their wine on</i>

1158
01:30:03,531 --> 01:30:06,659
<i>For your inspection, our cocktail collection</i>

1159
01:32:28,242 --> 01:32:31,643
<i>Clothes must play a part</i>

1160
01:32:31,746 --> 01:32:35,273
<i>To light an eye, to win a heart</i>

1161
01:32:35,349 --> 01:32:38,011
<i>They say a gown can almost speak</i>

1162
01:32:39,153 --> 01:32:41,644
<i>If it is chic</i>

1163
01:32:41,756 --> 01:32:46,284
<i>Should you select the right effect</i>
<i>you cannot miss</i>

1164
